<br>
Concentration does not matter if you are not in combat, but for combat casting it is extrememly important.  I'm not too sure how strict NWN is, but there are so many things in the tabletop game that can cause a spell to be distracted that it is definetly worth it if you need to cast spells mid battle.<br>
<br>
Fortitude is one extra hp per level.  On the surface its kind of useless, but I guess in the overall picture 20 extra hp's isn't so bad.<br>
<br>
Spellcraft lets you know what kind of caster you are facing.  At the early levels its uses are probably not as noticeable, and even later on its harder to see its usefullness as its so hard to &quot;quick react&quot; in nwn as everything is real time.  Its usefulness was in the table top game as you could know what your opponent was casting and actually have a bit to think of what to counter before you had to act.<br>
<br>
Alignment is only important for alignment restricted classes (paladins, monks, druids ... ) and the like, its also how some NPC's react to you.  In D&amp;D you have an aura of your alignment, evil creatures who can cast protection from aura can have protection from good up and you will have a harder time landing attack rolls.  I usually play good over evil as it is my style of play, of course, I usually save the game then wax merchants and other people who have pissed me off, reload and go back on my way so maybe I'm doing it just to get all the phat lewt quests. =/ <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumfrm42.showPrevMessage?topicID=36.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumfrm42.showNextMessage?topicID=36.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumfrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=36.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.unbeliever.net/images/lanys/postreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumfrm42.emailToFriend?topicID=36.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumfrm42.threadControl?topicID=36.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumfrm42.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=36.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumfrm42.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=36.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td 